{"tid":1270093,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"建議大家去圖書館搵呢本書","createTime":"2019-06-30T18:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T18:20:05.000Z","uid":77547,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7bfa4230971a7e5152b2f69ba21b02c76b96cca","tid":1270093,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Resilience-Science-Mastering-Greatest-Challenges/dp/1108441661/ref=dp_ob_title_bk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FResilience-Science-Mastering-Greatest-Challenges%2Fdp%2F1108441661%2Fref%3Ddp_ob_title_bk&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edP5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=3218a3fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Resilience-Science-Mastering-Greatest-Challenges/dp/1108441661/ref=dp_ob_title_bk</a><br />\n<br />\n香港最近發生既大事，又或者日常生活各種煩惱，都可能令到你心緒不寧。<br />\n<br />\nResilience，即係抗逆力咁解。書入面有提，有時一啲好壞既情況，反而令我地成長，知道面對困難時候應該點樣快速回復過黎。我早排睇呢本書，咁岩撞正屋企人精神病發，睇完呢本書，我了解到有咩途徑可以捱過呢場仗。<br />\n<br />\n有啲諷刺地，教育局都有呢個topic既介紹，真係多謝你既教育呀。<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/teacher/student-guidance-discipline-services/lecture-notes/lecture-notes-201718/20171219_EP_Tom_LAM.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fteacher%2Fstudent-guidance-discipline-services%2Flecture-notes%2Flecture-notes-201718%2F20171219_EP_Tom_LAM.pdf&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edP5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=30a448be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/teacher/student-guidance-discipline-services/lecture-notes/lecture-notes-201718/20171219_EP_Tom_LAM.pdf</a>"}]}